   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["# Regression Test Framework\n**Compares tables between `biw` and `biw_sf` schemas in Unity Catalog.**\n\n## How to use\n1. Upload your config CSV to DBFS\n2. Set widget values below (or pass via Jobs API)\n3. Run all cells\n4. Check HTML report at `html_output_path` and Delta tables in `caife_utils`\n\n## Widget reference\n| Widget | Description | Example |\n|---|---|---|\n| `catalog` | Unity Catalog name | `uc_dev0004` |\n| `source_catalog` | Source catalog (if cross-tenant) | `uc_dev0004` |\n| `target_catalog` | Target catalog (if cross-tenant) | `uc_dev0004` |\n| `source_schema` | Source schema | `biw` |\n| `target_schema` | Target schema | `biw_sf` |\n| `output_schema` | Output Delta tables schema | `caife_utils` |\n| `csv_path` | Path to config CSV | `/dbfs/configs/regression.csv` |\n| `html_output_path` | Path to write HTML report | `/dbfs/reports/` |\n| `max_workers` | Parallel table workers | `4` |\n| `webhook_url` | Webhook URL for failure alerts | `https://...` |\n| `row_count_threshold` | Warn + skip if rows exceed this and no partition | `50000000` |"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
